						               													<description>MadMobz is a card game that revolves around the idea of rival mobz. Every player commands a different mob, each with their own house, business and car. Everyone has action cards (such as an attack, defend, swat, etc.) with different characteristics and have to properly use them in order to win. The players have to deal with ripdeals, snitches, SWAT teams, gold diggers, hustlers as well as other possible obstacles. In order to win, each participant has to manage resources and eliminate the rival mobz.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How do you play MadMobz?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Choose your infamous gang! Who are you? The Chicago Boss, The Sicilian Family, The Mexican Cartel, The NY Connection, The Cuban Stars, The Colombian King, or The Black Widow.&amp;#10;     Put your gang members in the right place and take out all other gangs!&amp;#10;     Make sure to attack their car, business and home to take out the Gangleader!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game has 88 playing cards and 40 team cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Playing Cards:&amp;#10;In the game, there are attack cards with which you have to take out the other gangs, which can be defended with defence cards such as 'defend'.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With the action cards, you can bully the gangs by, for example, placing the 'Alliance' card between 2 gangs (their fate is now the same). Block these nasty plague cards with the 'Get the F *ck out' card!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game also has 'super cards' such as 'Earthquake' to destroy all houses or Frankenstein to bring a defeated gang member back to life.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you want to take out the gangs with a good blow, start a GangWar.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
